1
00:01:31,100 --> 00:01:34,980
=Wonder Wall=

2
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,910
=Episode 14=

3
00:02:19,479 --> 00:02:20,319
Happy Birthday!

4
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,000
Happy Birthday.

5
00:02:29,476 --> 00:02:34,148
(2018)

6
00:02:39,639 --> 00:02:40,400
Zinuo,

7
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:43,000
from now on, eat whatever you want.

8
00:02:43,919 --> 00:02:44,919
She won't control you anymore.

9
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:46,039
Starting today,

10
00:02:46,039 --> 00:02:47,039
you're an adult.

11
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:48,479
You have to

12
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,800
make your own decisions.

13
00:02:51,439 --> 00:02:52,280
And you have to learn

14
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,080
to walk your own path.

15
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,879
But no matter what,

16
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:59,000
I'll always support you

17
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,080
from behind.

18
00:03:01,199 --> 00:03:02,560
Okay. Come on, eat.

19
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:07,120
It's good.

20
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:02,919
Go back to sleep.

21
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,120
It's not right.

22
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:09,759
That's not the taste.

23
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:20,600
Zinuo.

24
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:22,759
Zinuo, are you okay?

25
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:24,360
What's wrong?

26
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:30,360
Zinuo.

27
00:04:32,279 --> 00:04:33,079
Are you okay?

28
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:43,560
Are you okay?

29
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,560
Need some medicine?

30
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,120
What's the matter?

31
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,240
What's wrong?

32
00:04:52,519 --> 00:04:53,040
Zinuo.

33
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,399
♪Work hard and make money♪

34
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:50,839
♪I want to get rich♪

35
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:53,000
(Tiezhu)
♪A villa by the sea♪

36
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:54,560
(Tiezhu)
♪Seafood every day♪

37
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,399
♪Fancy cars, pick what I want♪

38
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,279
Hello.

39
00:05:58,399 --> 00:05:59,959
Hello. Ming, open the door.

40
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,279
What are you doing here?

41
00:06:01,319 --> 00:06:02,959
Didn't you tell us to come?

42
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,720
There is a big guy at the door.

43
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,480
Did you see him?

44
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,480
Yes.

45
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,959
He's just lying there.

46
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,160
Is he asleep?

47
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:12,000
I'll tell you the password.

48
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:12,800
Come in quietly.

49
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,000
Don't wake him up.

50
00:06:14,199 --> 00:06:14,800
Otherwise,

51
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,120
it's going to get ugly.

52
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,199
Alright.

53
00:06:21,079 --> 00:06:22,199
Sleeping like a pig.

54
00:06:22,199 --> 00:06:23,319
Some surveillance this is.

55
00:06:23,879 --> 00:06:25,120
Not professional at all.

56
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,000
Stop blabbering.

57
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:28,680
Let's go.

58
00:06:38,879 --> 00:06:40,160
It's all here.

59
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,480
If you don't trust me,

60
00:06:42,519 --> 00:06:43,399
you can count it.

61
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:44,160
Two million total.

62
00:06:44,279 --> 00:06:44,920
No need.

63
00:06:45,639 --> 00:06:46,519
Here's the receipt.

64
00:06:46,879 --> 00:06:47,560
Fingerprint here.

65
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:51,160
Here.

66
00:06:51,792 --> 00:06:53,356
(Personal Statement)
(Certificate)

67
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:54,800
Mr. Yu.

68
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:56,759
Ms. Wen.

69
00:06:58,920 --> 00:06:59,800
You're so kind.

70
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:00,560
Give it to me.

71
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:03,480
Is it all there?

72
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:05,439
Yes.

73
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:08,759
How about we treat you to dinner?

74
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,800
No need. We've eaten.

75
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:10,639
You may go.

76
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,920
I'll take you

77
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:12,839
to the second floor.

78
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:13,839
Let's

79
00:07:14,079 --> 00:07:14,839
- go?
- Go.

80
00:07:15,079 --> 00:07:15,759
Let's go.

81
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:29,199
Where are you going?

82
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,360
This way.

83
00:07:37,439 --> 00:07:37,839
Zhu,

84
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,759
is two million cash so small in size?

85
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,160
Fits in two bags?

86
00:07:42,959 --> 00:07:43,399
Zhu,

87
00:07:44,399 --> 00:07:46,079
this two million is heavy.

88
00:07:46,959 --> 00:07:48,120
My shoulders are killing me.

89
00:07:48,639 --> 00:07:49,199
Zhu,

90
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:51,199
I'm still shaking.

91
00:07:51,519 --> 00:07:52,759
How could they

92
00:07:52,759 --> 00:07:53,800
just give us two million like that?

93
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:54,879
It feels like a dream.

94
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,800
Stop blabbering.

95
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,279
What if someone hears us?

96
00:07:57,399 --> 00:07:57,759
Alright.

97
00:07:57,759 --> 00:07:58,319
Now hurry up.

98
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:58,759
Go.

99
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,000
♪Work hard and make money♪

100
00:08:08,199 --> 00:08:09,439
♪I want to get rich♪

101
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,759
♪A villa by the sea♪

102
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,319
♪Seafood every day♪

103
00:08:14,399 --> 00:08:14,879
Hello.

104
00:08:15,079 --> 00:08:15,639
Yu Ming,

105
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:18,439
come to my car dealership tomorrow.

106
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,199
What for?

107
00:08:20,839 --> 00:08:21,959
You'll know when you come.

108
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:30,319
It sings day and night.

109
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:32,240
Gives me such a fright.

110
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,799
That thing is gone today, alright.

111
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:34,919
Bring you weapon.

112
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:35,720
See if Hong Jinkui

113
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,360
is still there.

114
00:08:49,279 --> 00:08:49,759
He has left.

115
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,519
Come on, take it slow.

116
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,320
- One, two, three.
- Okay.

117
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,759
Turn it.

118
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:09,559
Okay now.

119
00:09:10,519 --> 00:09:10,960
Alright.

120
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,159
It looks pretty.

121
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:33,960
Welcome, Mr. Yu!

122
00:09:47,159 --> 00:09:48,159
Why did you ask me to come?

123
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:53,080
Before Almighty God

124
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,600
and all

125
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,799
who stand here today,

126
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:58,039
I make this oath.

127
00:09:58,440 --> 00:09:58,960
Today,

128
00:09:59,159 --> 00:10:00,759
I want to take

129
00:10:00,799 --> 00:10:01,840
the man who saved my son and me,

130
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,759
Mr. Yu Ming,

131
00:10:02,799 --> 00:10:04,559
as my godfather.

132
00:10:05,759 --> 00:10:07,000
As my sworn brother.

133
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:07,879
From now on,

134
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:10,080
We share honor and disgrace,
life and death.

135
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,720
My shop is yours.

136
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,600
My car is yours.

137
00:10:19,919 --> 00:10:20,440
Pick one.

138
00:10:40,039 --> 00:10:40,879
I... I have things to do.

139
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:42,240
I should go.

140
00:10:45,879 --> 00:10:47,519
He did his deed and left,

141
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:50,039
seeking neither fame nor glory.

142
00:10:51,559 --> 00:10:53,919
Do a great favor without expecting
any reward in return.

143
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,960
That's why I believed in him.

144
00:10:58,519 --> 00:11:01,320
The sea may be cold,
but a warm heart makes up for it.

145
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:03,480
(School Awards Ceremony)
Your heroic deed

146
00:11:03,799 --> 00:11:06,120
(School Awards Ceremony)
not only saved two lives

147
00:11:06,639 --> 00:11:08,240
but also showed us

148
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:10,240
what true goodness looks like.

149
00:11:10,639 --> 00:11:12,960
Thank you for your selfless bravery.

150
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:15,120
On a beautiful, sunny day,

151
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:17,360
you became a warrior.

152
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,519
With strength and wisdom,

153
00:11:19,519 --> 00:11:20,799
you raced against time

154
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,559
and fought against death itself

155
00:11:22,919 --> 00:11:24,360
to rescue us

156
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:26,000
from the grip

157
00:11:26,039 --> 00:11:27,200
of danger.

158
00:11:27,519 --> 00:11:29,399
You are an everyday hero.

159
00:11:29,639 --> 00:11:31,879
A true guardian.

160
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:36,919
Students,

161
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:38,480
Yu Wenwen's father

162
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:40,360
is an everyday hero,

163
00:11:40,639 --> 00:11:42,399
ordinary, but extraordinary.

164
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:11,919
Wenwen,

165
00:12:12,399 --> 00:12:13,080
congratulations!

166
00:12:14,799 --> 00:12:15,080
Okay.

167
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:17,000
Now let's welcome Yu Wenwen

168
00:12:17,159 --> 00:12:18,240
to give us a speech.

169
00:12:23,679 --> 00:12:25,080
Mom, tell dad to come back!

170
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:25,840
Tell him to come back!

171
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:26,440
He is out of strength.

172
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:40,360
Wenwen.

173
00:12:51,831 --> 00:12:55,155
(To Mr. Yu Ming - A hero of our time.
Selfless courage. Eternal gratitude.)

174
00:12:57,799 --> 00:12:59,399
Why do I have to give a speech?

175
00:12:59,679 --> 00:13:01,159
I almost lost my dad!

176
00:13:01,799 --> 00:13:02,639
Wu Xiaoxuan,

177
00:13:02,679 --> 00:13:03,720
don't think you can live long

178
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:05,039
just because your family is rich.

179
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,000
Yu Wenwen,

180
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,480
you're a hero's daughter.

181
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:09,480
You aren't supposed to fight.

182
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:11,480
I'll go.

183
00:13:12,919 --> 00:13:13,480
Are you okay?

184
00:13:13,639 --> 00:13:14,480
It doesn't hurt.

185
00:13:14,879 --> 00:13:15,600
I'm fine.

186
00:13:16,279 --> 00:13:17,440
Stop laughing!

187
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:18,879
Don't laugh!

188
00:13:18,879 --> 00:13:19,600
Stop laughing!

189
00:13:20,039 --> 00:13:20,919
Yes.

190
00:13:21,519 --> 00:13:22,320
I'm truly sorry.

191
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:22,919
Ms. Zhou,

192
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:24,799
We keep putting you out.

193
00:13:25,639 --> 00:13:26,320
Yes.

194
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:27,399
We'll calm her down.

195
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:28,759
We will do it.

196
00:13:29,039 --> 00:13:29,799
It's just

197
00:13:29,799 --> 00:13:31,120
she is too stubborn.

198
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:35,879
Why are you back?

199
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:37,679
School gave her half a day off.

200
00:13:40,639 --> 00:13:41,240
Perfect.

201
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:42,559
Jiang.

202
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:43,639
Jiang.

203
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:45,240
Don't freeze the beef.

204
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:46,440
We're cooking it now.

205
00:13:46,519 --> 00:13:47,519
I'll help you out.

206
00:13:47,639 --> 00:13:48,120
Alright.

207
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,639
Everyone's been praising dad today.

208
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:51,879
Why are you unhappy?

209
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:54,120
They kept talking about it.

210
00:13:54,399 --> 00:13:55,320
When I think of that day,

211
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,279
I feel really awful.

212
00:13:57,159 --> 00:13:57,799
It feels like...

213
00:13:59,919 --> 00:14:00,679
It feels like

214
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:02,879
my heart is jumping to my throat.

215
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,720
It's just very painful.

216
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:06,799
You know,

217
00:14:06,799 --> 00:14:07,840
your way of expressing things.

218
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:09,080
I should hire you a language teacher.

219
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,080
How about that?

220
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:11,279
She's way better than I am.

221
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:13,759
Let me ask you, why did you

222
00:14:13,759 --> 00:14:15,000
pull Wu Xiaoxuan's ear today?

223
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:15,960
What did he do to you?

224
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,759
I said I was a bulletproof vest.

225
00:14:18,159 --> 00:14:19,200
Whatever his dad did

226
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,399
will bounce right back to him.

227
00:14:20,399 --> 00:14:21,399
He's lucky I didn't beat him up.

228
00:14:21,559 --> 00:14:22,559
And now you really can't.

229
00:14:22,559 --> 00:14:23,360
Your principal says

230
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,440
you've got an image now.

231
00:14:24,559 --> 00:14:25,240
You're the daughter

232
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:26,440
of a hero.

233
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:27,799
So you can't get into fights.

234
00:14:29,799 --> 00:14:31,080
See? Your dad can't take a compliment.

235
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:33,480
A hero's child can't beat others.

236
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:35,480
Does that child have no feelings?

237
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:36,399
No anger allowed.

238
00:14:36,519 --> 00:14:37,279
Yeah.

239
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:39,279
People have feelings.

240
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:41,200
You can't just
shut them down completely.

241
00:14:41,279 --> 00:14:42,480
Whatever happens,

242
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:43,840
you react accordingly.

243
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,559
If someone hits you, you hit back.

244
00:14:45,799 --> 00:14:46,799
If they don't,

245
00:14:47,039 --> 00:14:48,320
what if they get beaten to death?

246
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,720
Just look at yourself.

247
00:14:54,799 --> 00:14:55,759
Let me

248
00:14:55,759 --> 00:14:56,440
wash the pot later.

249
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:01,519
Mr. Yu,

250
00:15:01,799 --> 00:15:02,639
you are really something.

251
00:15:02,679 --> 00:15:03,879
I heard your mom tell me about it.

252
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:05,919
It scared me half to death.

253
00:15:06,039 --> 00:15:07,120
That was terrifying.

254
00:15:07,559 --> 00:15:08,799
He was like a coiled spring.

255
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:09,240
and then

256
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:10,000
he sprang out.

257
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,279
Aren't you afraid of drowning?

258
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:12,720
Mr. Yu,

259
00:15:13,159 --> 00:15:13,960
from great peril

260
00:15:14,039 --> 00:15:14,759
comes great fortune.

261
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,840
Welcome. This way, please.

262
00:15:25,399 --> 00:15:26,120
What do you mean?

263
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:27,480
Stop being so paranoid.

264
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:29,120
I'm working. Can't you see?

265
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:32,200
Tomorrow,

266
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,240
dads and moms will be back.

267
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,039
Let's have dinner together.

268
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:34,799
I have no time.

269
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:38,080
See that guy at the counter?

270
00:15:38,919 --> 00:15:40,600
I'm eighty percent there.

271
00:15:40,759 --> 00:15:42,240
Tomorrow, we'll watch a movie together.

272
00:15:43,039 --> 00:15:44,519
This could be a big night.

273
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:45,240
No way

274
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:46,720
am I letting a family dinner ruin it.

275
00:15:46,879 --> 00:15:48,519
What would you like to drink?
It's on me.

276
00:15:49,519 --> 00:15:50,480
I don't want anything.

277
00:15:51,399 --> 00:15:52,200
Fine. I'm off.

278
00:15:52,279 --> 00:15:53,000
Wait a moment.

279
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:54,080
I have a question.

280
00:15:54,399 --> 00:15:55,120
Sit down first.

281
00:15:58,840 --> 00:16:00,360
What is it? Hurry up.

282
00:16:01,919 --> 00:16:03,000
I took your advice

283
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:04,559
and made her a bowl of noodles.

284
00:16:05,879 --> 00:16:06,519
But she threw up.

285
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:07,679
She threw up?

286
00:16:08,679 --> 00:16:09,759
Was it that bad?

287
00:16:09,799 --> 00:16:11,440
She didn't even eat it.

288
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:12,679
She looked at it and got sick.

289
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:14,440
Then I doubt

290
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,120
it's the noodles.

291
00:16:16,279 --> 00:16:16,799
What?

292
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:17,519
Maybe it's me.

293
00:16:17,639 --> 00:16:18,240
Could be.

294
00:16:18,360 --> 00:16:20,279
It means you don't really know her yet.

295
00:16:20,399 --> 00:16:21,399
What should I do now?

