00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:36,960
Right now,

595
00:28:37,559 --> 00:28:38,920
she wants to use it

596
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:39,880
to blackmail me.

597
00:28:39,960 --> 00:28:40,519
Well,

598
00:28:40,720 --> 00:28:41,440
what should we do now?

599
00:28:41,640 --> 00:28:42,920
Just wait and see.

600
00:28:43,519 --> 00:28:45,880
First, let's see
what she will ask from us.

601
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:03,440
Is that Li Jin?

602
00:29:04,799 --> 00:29:05,680
She has been released?

603
00:29:08,417 --> 00:29:09,904
(Li Jin Verdict:
Guilty of Embezzlement, Five Years)

604
00:29:11,880 --> 00:29:13,039
It really is Li Jin.

605
00:29:16,640 --> 00:29:17,839
So she's out now.

606
00:30:07,160 --> 00:30:10,640
♪Cuckoo♪

607
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:14,400
♪It has a quick temper♪

608
00:30:15,039 --> 00:30:17,920
♪It becomes impatient in spring♪

609
00:30:18,799 --> 00:30:21,440
♪Cuckoo, cuckoo, never stopping♪

610
00:30:31,839 --> 00:30:32,480
That clock.

611
00:30:32,799 --> 00:30:33,400
Cuckoo, cuckoo.

612
00:30:33,799 --> 00:30:34,240
That clock.

613
00:30:34,240 --> 00:30:34,960
The Black Forest Clock.

614
00:30:36,799 --> 00:30:37,519
Could your dad

615
00:30:37,640 --> 00:30:38,519
have hidden any clues

616
00:30:38,519 --> 00:30:39,240
in it?

617
00:30:41,359 --> 00:30:41,880
What's wrong?

618
00:30:42,039 --> 00:30:43,359
That clock has been thrown away.

619
00:30:43,440 --> 00:30:44,279
It kept going off randomly.

620
00:30:44,279 --> 00:30:45,240
So we threw it out.

621
00:30:45,240 --> 00:30:46,559
Where did you throw it?

622
00:30:58,720 --> 00:31:00,000
I want to see that money again.

623
00:31:01,440 --> 00:31:02,119
I want to see

624
00:31:02,119 --> 00:31:03,240
what kind of power it has.

625
00:31:04,680 --> 00:31:06,200
That made my dad trade his life for it.

626
00:31:30,519 --> 00:31:31,160
Oh, no.

627
00:31:33,759 --> 00:31:34,279
Sir,

628
00:31:34,640 --> 00:31:35,799
may I ask you something?

629
00:31:36,079 --> 00:31:37,079
We threw away

630
00:31:37,079 --> 00:31:37,880
a clock here.

631
00:31:37,880 --> 00:31:38,920
Do you know where it went?

632
00:31:39,319 --> 00:31:40,279
The garbage here

633
00:31:40,279 --> 00:31:41,759
all goes to the dump east of city.

634
00:31:42,039 --> 00:31:42,880
All the garbage

635
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:43,559
from this community

636
00:31:43,559 --> 00:31:45,000
all goes to the east city dump?

637
00:31:45,319 --> 00:31:45,599
Yes.

638
00:31:45,599 --> 00:31:46,480
Okay, thank you.

639
00:31:50,680 --> 00:31:52,200
You young people nowadays

640
00:31:52,519 --> 00:31:53,160
toss things away

641
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:54,519
whenever you're upset.

642
00:31:55,240 --> 00:31:56,200
And then afterward

643
00:31:56,640 --> 00:31:57,279
you regret it.

644
00:31:58,559 --> 00:31:59,119
Remember,

645
00:31:59,559 --> 00:32:00,279
When you're

646
00:32:00,759 --> 00:32:01,519
done searching,

647
00:32:01,519 --> 00:32:02,720
put them all back neatly.

648
00:32:02,880 --> 00:32:03,519
Okay.

649
00:32:03,799 --> 00:32:04,319
Don't be like

650
00:32:04,319 --> 00:32:05,079
those guys this morning.

651
00:32:06,039 --> 00:32:07,400
There were people here this morning?

652
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:09,599
A man and a woman came in the morning,

653
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:10,920
brought about a dozen people.

654
00:32:10,960 --> 00:32:11,880
Quite a big scene.

655
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:12,599
Oh, right.

656
00:32:12,640 --> 00:32:13,880
They were also looking for something

657
00:32:13,880 --> 00:32:14,759
sent from your Ziyu Garden.

658
00:32:15,039 --> 00:32:16,039
Their car

659
00:32:16,279 --> 00:32:17,079
was so shiny

660
00:32:17,240 --> 00:32:17,960
and looked very fancy.

661
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:19,319
They seem to be quite rich.

662
00:32:19,839 --> 00:32:20,400
What could they

663
00:32:20,400 --> 00:32:21,400
have lost on earth?

664
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:22,200
They can just

665
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:22,960
buy a new one.

666
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:24,079
Being so wealthy,

667
00:32:24,119 --> 00:32:25,599
why must they go
to all this effort here?

668
00:33:00,759 --> 00:33:01,640
When they said Chen Liyang

669
00:33:01,640 --> 00:33:02,599
was a huge embezzler,

670
00:33:04,880 --> 00:33:05,680
I didn't believe it.

671
00:33:08,759 --> 00:33:09,880
Even if he did embezzle,

672
00:33:11,680 --> 00:33:13,160
Li Jin must have pushed him into it.

673
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:18,079
But now

674
00:33:22,599 --> 00:33:23,559
I'm not so sure anymore.

675
00:33:31,079 --> 00:33:32,400
When I reported Li Jin,

676
00:33:34,640 --> 00:33:35,359
I never thought things

677
00:33:35,359 --> 00:33:36,359
would blow up like this.

678
00:33:37,759 --> 00:33:39,480
I thought if she just went
to prison for a few years,

679
00:33:40,920 --> 00:33:42,440
my dad and I could finally
get some peace.

680
00:33:46,319 --> 00:33:47,960
Even after everything fell apart,

681
00:33:50,599 --> 00:33:51,680
I never thought my dad

682
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:52,559
was part of it.

683
00:33:54,359 --> 00:33:55,359
Li Jin was right.

684
00:33:57,039 --> 00:33:57,880
I was wrong.

685
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:03,359
I misjudged people.

686
00:34:05,039 --> 00:34:05,799
I used to think

687
00:34:05,799 --> 00:34:07,039
he was a good father.

688
00:34:08,079 --> 00:34:09,800
But he made the same mistakes

689
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:11,159
as Li Jin.

690
00:34:11,960 --> 00:34:13,000
He paid his life

691
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:16,280
to get this money.

692
00:34:19,519 --> 00:34:21,320
Just how useless am I

693
00:34:22,480 --> 00:34:23,480
that he'd find a way out

694
00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:24,639
for me like this?

695
00:34:33,320 --> 00:34:33,920
I know what my dad

696
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:35,159
has left me now.

697
00:34:41,239 --> 00:34:42,400
It's the evidence

698
00:34:43,960 --> 00:34:45,480
enough to send Li Jin
back to prison again.

699
00:34:51,800 --> 00:34:52,800
He wanted to protect me.

700
00:34:54,599 --> 00:34:55,880
He was afraid Li Jin would hurt me.

701
00:35:02,199 --> 00:35:03,360
My dad handed me the blade.

702
00:35:04,760 --> 00:35:05,320
Zinuo,

703
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:07,440
don't dwell on this right now.

704
00:35:08,519 --> 00:35:10,320
We'll definitely find a solution.

705
00:35:11,639 --> 00:35:12,320
Trust me.

706
00:35:23,559 --> 00:35:24,079
Ming.

707
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:25,599
Li Jin already came by.

708
00:35:25,960 --> 00:35:27,000
She took it away.

709
00:35:31,639 --> 00:35:32,159
Got it.

710
00:35:34,639 --> 00:35:35,239
That's right.

711
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:38,159
That's just like her.

712
00:36:08,960 --> 00:36:10,000
Go buy me a bottle of water.

713
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:11,280
Okay.

714
00:37:11,119 --> 00:37:12,360
Everything you cherished

715
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:14,360
are all here.

716
00:37:24,123 --> 00:37:26,277
(Tomb of Chen Liyang)

717
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:27,000
Chen Liyang,

718
00:37:28,159 --> 00:37:29,119
from today on,

719
00:37:30,280 --> 00:37:31,480
we're even.

720
00:38:07,159 --> 00:38:07,760
Mr. Chen,

721
00:38:08,639 --> 00:38:09,280
sorry about this.

722
00:38:55,880 --> 00:38:56,639
What are you thinking?

723
00:38:59,039 --> 00:39:00,159
Li Jin ocne said

724
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:02,880
my heart is as hard

725
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:03,800
as a stone.

726
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:06,360
I think she was right.

727
00:39:10,159 --> 00:39:11,599
We are the same by nature.

728
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:13,639
Just as cold,

729
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:15,599
just as selfish.

730
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:21,159
The harder I try to escape her,

731
00:39:22,920 --> 00:39:23,760
the more I turn into her.

732
00:39:25,119 --> 00:39:26,079
In the end, even I

733
00:39:26,079 --> 00:39:26,960
can't stand myself.

734
00:39:31,199 --> 00:39:32,400
Don't hate yourself.

735
00:39:33,400 --> 00:39:34,280
You should love yourself.

736
00:39:36,840 --> 00:39:38,199
Whatever makes you happy,

737
00:39:38,199 --> 00:39:39,039
hold on to it.

738
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:41,079
Whatever makes you suffer,

739
00:39:41,239 --> 00:39:42,239
either forget it

740
00:39:42,599 --> 00:39:43,719
or get through it.

741
00:39:58,920 --> 00:39:59,360
Haven't

742
00:39:59,360 --> 00:40:00,559
felt this light in ages.

743
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:02,719
That's how it should be.

744
00:40:04,280 --> 00:40:05,199
Actually, I don't think

745
00:40:05,400 --> 00:40:06,719
you have to carry so much.

746
00:40:07,599 --> 00:40:08,760
You don't know what happened

747
00:40:08,760 --> 00:40:09,519
between them.

748
00:40:10,280 --> 00:40:11,639
And it's them who made the mistakes.

749
00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:13,280
That's not on you.

750
00:40:14,760 --> 00:40:15,760
You should learn to let it go.

751
00:40:21,719 --> 00:40:22,760
I can't be as selfless

752
00:40:23,599 --> 00:40:24,840
as my father,

753
00:40:26,559 --> 00:40:27,079
and I can't learn

754
00:40:27,079 --> 00:40:28,360
to be as selfish as my mother.

755
00:40:29,639 --> 00:40:30,440
Being stuck in between.

756
00:40:31,239 --> 00:40:32,079
That's what's so painful.

757
00:40:34,199 --> 00:40:34,920
A change of place

758
00:40:35,239 --> 00:40:36,119
would do you good.

759
00:40:36,280 --> 00:40:36,960
Out of sight,

760
00:40:36,960 --> 00:40:38,239
out of mind.

761
00:40:40,920 --> 00:40:41,559
Actually, I want

762
00:40:41,559 --> 00:40:42,519
to go see my senior.

763
00:40:44,760 --> 00:40:46,039
Every time, I feel lost,

764
00:40:47,239 --> 00:40:48,440
she always knows how to guide me.

765
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:51,599
And when I'm with her,

766
00:40:52,599 --> 00:40:54,119
I feel a sense of calm.

767
00:40:54,480 --> 00:40:55,519
Isn't she in Germany?

768
00:40:57,760 --> 00:40:58,920
I said change your surroundings,

769
00:40:58,920 --> 00:41:00,280
not change your country.

770
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:05,880
How to say hello in German?

771
00:41:06,719 --> 00:41:07,360
Hello.

772
00:41:08,239 --> 00:41:10,119
Hello.

773
00:41:11,079 --> 00:41:12,079
How to say thank you?

774
00:41:13,639 --> 00:41:14,760
Why the sudden interest in German?

775
00:41:15,440 --> 00:41:16,920
If I have a chance to go there,

776
00:41:16,960 --> 00:41:17,719
I can use it.

777
00:41:23,199 --> 00:41:25,840
Thank you for being with me.

778
00:41:25,880 --> 00:41:27,639
Thank you.

779
00:41:28,199 --> 00:41:28,880
Thank you.

780
00:41:30,360 --> 00:41:30,880
Thank you.

781
00:41:31,880 --> 00:41:32,400
Thank you.

782
00:41:34,360 --> 00:41:35,400
It's quite a challenge.

783
00:41:43,078 --> 00:41:45,053
(Shengli Group
Equity Transfer Agreement)

784
00:41:47,952 --> 00:41:49,485
(Mingcheng Times Project
Settlement Agreement)

785
00:41:53,368 --> 00:41:54,572
(Shengli Group Fund Transfer Request)

786
00:41:57,607 --> 00:41:59,260
