787
00:41:59,333 --> 00:42:00,524
(Lixun Equipment
Procurement Supplier Recommendation)

788
00:42:11,718 --> 00:42:13,822
(Unknown Number)

789
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:21,400
Hello?

790
00:42:22,199 --> 00:42:24,480
Let me speak to Ms. Li Jin.

791
00:42:30,159 --> 00:42:30,719
Speak.

792
00:42:32,360 --> 00:42:34,159
I have something

793
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:35,880
that I'm sure

794
00:42:35,880 --> 00:42:37,199
you'll be very interested in.

795
00:42:37,559 --> 00:42:39,800
(Shengli Group Fund Transfer Request)
On July 11, 2009,

796
00:42:40,159 --> 00:42:41,920
One million yuan was transferred

797
00:42:41,960 --> 00:42:43,760
to Weifang Engineering Company.

798
00:42:43,800 --> 00:42:44,519
A shell company.

799
00:42:44,880 --> 00:42:46,199
No real business at all.

800
00:42:46,639 --> 00:42:48,079
In April, 2007,

801
00:42:48,800 --> 00:42:50,440
you dared fake bids

802
00:42:50,559 --> 00:42:52,079
for a fire safety renovation.

803
00:42:52,400 --> 00:42:53,039
Every company involved

804
00:42:53,039 --> 00:42:54,159
was a shell company.

805
00:42:55,000 --> 00:42:56,599
Your quotes were more than double

806
00:42:56,599 --> 00:42:57,840
the industry average.

807
00:42:57,840 --> 00:42:59,760
You've got some serious nerve!

808
00:43:05,080 --> 00:43:07,880
(Next Episode)

809
00:43:08,119 --> 00:43:09,320
(Actor, Guo Jingfei)
Hi, I'm Guo Jingfei.

810
00:43:09,320 --> 00:43:11,679
(Actor, Guo Jingfei)
I invite you to watch Wonder Wall.

811
00:43:14,239 --> 00:43:15,280
I'm not asking much.

812
00:43:15,639 --> 00:43:16,360
Fifty-fifty.

813
00:43:16,480 --> 00:43:17,079
No problem.

814
00:43:18,239 --> 00:43:19,159
Li Jin did it.

815
00:43:19,239 --> 00:43:20,280
She's the one who killed him.

816
00:43:20,559 --> 00:43:21,519
I agree.

817
00:43:21,679 --> 00:43:22,559
Hong Jinkui is one person.

818
00:43:22,679 --> 00:43:23,480
We are a whole family.

819
00:43:23,559 --> 00:43:24,559
If she doesn't die,

820
00:43:25,880 --> 00:43:27,320
we'll die.

821
00:43:27,400 --> 00:43:29,039
So what's our move?

822
00:43:29,440 --> 00:43:31,159
We're surrounded now.

823
00:43:31,280 --> 00:43:32,480
Everyone's after the money.

824
00:43:32,719 --> 00:43:33,800
Get the old woman and the kid

825
00:43:33,800 --> 00:43:34,480
out for me.

826
00:43:55,610 --> 00:44:02,620
♪The road ahead is still so long
Where have you gone?♪

827
00:44:04,180 --> 00:44:11,340
♪Under the blazing sun
I keep heading north♪

828
